    "monster1436": "<h1 class=monster>Red Dragon Wyrmling<br><span class=type>Medium natural magical beast (dragon)</span><br><span class=level>Level 5 Elite Soldier<span class=xp> XP 400</span></span> </h1> <p class=flavor><b>Initiative</b> +7        <b>Senses</b> Perception +9; Darkvision<br><b>HP</b> 134; <b>Bloodied</b> 67<br><b>AC</b> 23; <b>Fortitude</b> 21, <b>Reflex</b> 18, <b>Will</b> 17<br><b>Resist</b> 5 fire<br><b>Saving Throws</b> +2<br><b>Speed</b> 5, fly 7 (hover), overland flight 10<br><b>Action Points</b> 1</p><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Bite</b> (standard, at-will) ✦ <b>Fire</b></p><p class=flavorIndent>+13 vs AC; 2d6+6 fire damage. </p><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Claw</b> (standard, at-will) </p><p class=flavorIndent>+13 vs AC; 2d6+6 damage. </p><p class='flavor alt'>⚔ <b>Double Attack</b> (standard, at-will) </p><p class=flavorIndent>The wyrmling makes two claw attacks.</p><p class='flavor alt'>⚔ <b>Tall Strike</b> (immediate reaction, when an enemy moves to a position where it flanks the red dragon wyrmling, encounter) </p><p class=flavorIndent>The wyrmling attacks the triggering enemy with its tail; +11 vs Reflex; 1d10+6 damage, and the target is pushed 1 square. </p><p class='flavor alt'>ᗕ <b>Breath Weapon</b> (standard, recharges when first bloodied) </p><p class=flavorIndent>Close blast 5; +11 vs Reflex; 1d10+4 fire damage. Miss: Half damage. </p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Alignment</b> Evil       <b> Languages</b> Draconic<br><b>Skills</b> Bluff +8, Insight +9, Intimidate +8<br><b>Str</b> 22 (+8)      <b>Dex</b> 17 (+5)      <b>Wis</b> 14 (+4)<br><b>Con</b> 19 (+6)      <b>Int</b> 11 (+2)      <b>Cha</b> 12 (+3)</p><br><p class=publishedIn>Published in Draconomicon: Chromatic Dragons, page(s) 185.</p>",
